Package model

Class Product

java.lang.Object
model.Product
public class Product extends Object
This class contains all the details about the products. There are getters, setters and a toString method which are used for products' information processing.

    • Product

      public Product(int idProduct, String numeProdus, int cantitateDisponibila, int pretKilogram)
      This is a constructor with all the information a product must have - idProduct, numeProdus, cantitateDisponibila and pretKilogram.
      Parameters:
      idProduct - - a primary key (there is a validator for this)
      numeProdus - - the name of the product
      cantitateDisponibila - - the disposable quantity (there is a validator for this)
      pretKilogram - - the price per kilogram of a product (there is a validator for this)
